Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.65,0:02:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.55,0:02:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點不太對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.85,0:02:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.96,0:02:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.01,0:02:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有話想對你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.31,0:02:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.96,0:02:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.32,0:02:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.07,0:02:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.04,0:02:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比總
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.03,0:02:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如情報所說超級厲害的寶貝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不交給他們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.03,0:02:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們可是正在找這孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能交出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.01,0:02:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是我的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.58,0:03:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三唱 背叛了的七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都說了蕾不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推門進去一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.28,0:03:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被子 床 床 蕾她...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.23,0:03:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾可是被抓走了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是因為知道她是煌珠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.87,0:03:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話是這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是你們幹的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.37,0:03:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒禮貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.91,0:03:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 你們不是本來就衝著蕾來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.37,0:03:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是尋找煌珠的不只是我們哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.34,0:03:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要擁有巨大力量的煌珠的人至少有五萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶走蕾的恐怕就是其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個個都...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.48,0:04:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是為什麼只帶走蕾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也同樣是煌珠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.88,0:04:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是因為蕾更可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.37,0:04:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.90,0:04:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人是怎麼知道蕾的事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像知道些什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘了說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.75,0:04:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅餓了的話我們也管不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.51,0:04:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對...對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.51,0:04:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.06,0:04:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.43,0:04:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,違抗比總的話就無法在這鎮上生活下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.21,0:04:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比總
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.33,0:04:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌管這個城鎮的領主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.61,0:04:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是看到像守護翼的人來的話就要去通報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.49,0:04:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫比總的在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山...山上的城堡中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.40,0:04:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想一個人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.03,0:04:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別拿我當外行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.02,0:05:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是空賊紅山貓的下任老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會救出蕾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.93,0:05:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順利潛入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.65,0:05:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是本大爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.66,0:05:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.19,0:05:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.17,0:05:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被這...這種哄小孩的把戲幹掉的話就不叫酷大爺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 我不能輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.66,0:06:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡醒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.56,0:06:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內部情報沒錯的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該是很強的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為煌珠證明的核石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.17,0:06:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊 在那裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.19,0:07:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Erementar Gerad
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.63,0:07:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠都在身體的某個地方有一塊核石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.78,0:07:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那正是身為煌珠的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Erementar Gerad
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.58,0:07:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這塊石頭是真傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,粼光閃閃像要被吸入一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的東西見都沒見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很高興的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小女孩是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是真正的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你這個人造的檔次不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.59,0:07:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.49,0:07:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼看著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個人就什麼也幹不了的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.52,0:07:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要頂撞人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別拿我當外行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點找到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.12,0:08:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶著個有趣的生物嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.86,0:08:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.86,0:08:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一那樣的話就沒轍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.87,0:08:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來你在這幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.93,0:08:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.91,0:08:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊呀 這不是酷嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真巧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是很早就闖進來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然在這裏偶然相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.93,0:08:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶...偶然 不...不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我其實...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.88,0:08:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.29,0:08:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才還那麼豪言萬丈的酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.37,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能迷路了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.66,0:08:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那還用說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.10,0:08:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們又是來幹什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾的事和你們沒什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.59,0:08:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼能這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出門靠朋友 處世靠人情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然相處不久但已是同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相幫助是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.66,0:09:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說是這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.83,0:09:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算搶先救出蕾之後就溜得無影無蹤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.11,0:09:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能做那種事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.58,0:09:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.84,0:09:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不會做那麼卑鄙的事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底還是無法相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.69,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是絕對不會把蕾交給你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.64,0:09:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷了路這麼狼狽了還居然大言不慚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.53,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都說了 我怎麼可能迷路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行了 行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過不用擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.22,0:09:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.19,0:09:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼配備——煌珠偵測雷達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.82,0:09:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是個好東西 能偵測到方圓一千米之內的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣蕾的所在就一清二楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.43,0:09:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就事不宜遲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是當前位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.49,0:09:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個紅點是奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.42,0:09:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個綠點顯示了蕾的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.08,0:10:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從蕾被抓走這點看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.35,0:10:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方肯定是訂立契約之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.56,0:10:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.95,0:10:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有守護翼的保證——奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.76,0:10:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去哪了 那女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅 喂 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看...看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃的一大堆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候你這種人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.69,0:10:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方若是煌珠同契者的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.08,0:10:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許可能不得不戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.99,0:10:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要讓奇雅發威不讓她吃飽的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了 隨你們的便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去救蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 把雷達還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.78,0:10:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走掉了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.00,0:10:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與其和那種冒冒失失亂來的人聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.32,0:10:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不如我們救出蕾之後把她帶回去好一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.83,0:10:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.65,0:10:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錢 地位 名譽 錢都能稱心如意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.39,0:11:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然想的是那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.15,0:11:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且錢還說了兩次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.25,0:11:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 這該不會是你們的宵夜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.95,0:11:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是 我們中圈套了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.22,0:11:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼教養的寵物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂啊 小浣熊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.64,0:11:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.88,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓吃飽喝足心情不錯的我好好疼疼你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.32,0:11:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吧 龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.17,0:11:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就請動手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡量不要客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當誘餌是吧 瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.43,0:11:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.11,0:11:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.38,0:11:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雄心之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.95,0:11:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懷抱大智
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,締結契約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如人所願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.63,0:12:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大鬧一番吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.21,0:12:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.91,0:12:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等著 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在就來救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.92,0:12:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.86,0:12:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉打擾你的興致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過好像有隻老鼠混進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.21,0:12:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.31,0:12:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道是誰但別想活著回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走 帕爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.00,0:12:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.87,0:13:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.97,0:13:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前還沒件像樣的兵器的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一下子就能戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是很高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底還是...人類...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.71,0:13:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來救你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒被動手動腳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.83,0:13:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.24,0:13:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.91,0:13:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那還用說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.90,0:13:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾被抓了所以來救你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.01,0:14:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.98,0:14:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.87,0:14:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事...吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那個 這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.71,0:14:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你這是在幹什麼 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.90,0:14:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.32,0:14:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是炮火的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.92,0:14:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 喂 龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再壯觀點打飛上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是好像過火了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩個傢伙是守護翼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.09,0:14:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.08,0:14:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.91,0:14:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是來找那孩子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.53,0:14:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用理會長鬃尾熊早點走掉就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.91,0:14:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩個傢伙好像是故意在這打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.25,0:14:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.71,0:14:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是誘餌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.93,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種非常時刻到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣說也不用拿槍揍我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總比一槍斃了你要好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.37,0:15:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.14,0:15:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多少考慮一下現在的處境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏可是敵人的城堡之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有蕾的力量在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.72,0:15:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.85,0:15:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是氣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那點小伎倆就想騙倒我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.50,0:15:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帕爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.45,0:15:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嫉妒以至痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搭上激流為箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,締結契約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷達上沒反應啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.32,0:15:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.07,0:15:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼號螺旋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.93,0:15:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是煌珠同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.99,0:16:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把蕾還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.55,0:16:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也看到那個男人已經同契了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏還是交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.97,0:16:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的搭擋是擬煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.36,0:16:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擬煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擬煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.76,0:16:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是指與蕾、奇雅等不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.33,0:16:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有人造核石的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.61,0:16:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將擬造核石嵌入人類少女體內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.44,0:16:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使人具有煌珠的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.26,0:16:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那對人的生命構成威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,需要下很大的決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.97,0:16:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要做這樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.45,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.21,0:16:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.06,0:16:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比總想要力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.14,0:16:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想成為他的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.88,0:16:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我心甘情願地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.03,0:16:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.56,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.55,0:17:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙只是為了被我們使用才生存的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.67,0:17:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是那樣的道具而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.36,0:17:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說八道什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.05,0:17:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾不是什麼道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.02,0:17:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.80,0:17:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.91,0:17:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.62,0:17:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才也
